{
  "stem": "4247.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he somehow managed to, to, to hang onto his bakery in Budapest, which was a good one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was exempted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By that time in Budapest, Jews have been also moved into certain areas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were so-called protected houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because by that time, the Swedish and the Swiss Embassy started some rescue activity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You might have heard of Raoul Wallenberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was one of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have-- they have effectively, by that time, established some very worthwhile rescue operation on international basis.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jewish internal resistance was still in the more localized Zionist front, right, who by that time, managed to get-- I imagine, I, I have no figures in mind, but I imagine, a good few hundred people through Romania out to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- I had-- I had the opportunity at that time-- I went to my, my, my battalion leader, to the lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said that I would like to provide some special bread for the battalion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he allowed me to go every day to my uncle's bakery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I brought two big baskets full of goodies for him, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that allowed-- that, that, that was very good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eventually, he allowed me to live outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, for a few weeks, I had an outside [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] task to perform.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I, I, I actually slept at my-- at my auntie's place, right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every morning, I went to my uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I got the basket full of, of bread rolls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I took it to the-- back to the-- to the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I lived outside for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
